text: Lacmellea edulis, common name: chicle muyu, is a species of tree in the family Apocynaceae native to Panama, Colombia, Venezuela, Brazil, Peru and Ecuador.Plants of the World Online (KEW) ==References== ==External links== *Lacmellea edulis at Useful Tropical Plants.
